     H            Y.
     F** UEXR41A ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET ORDER QTY FROM ABTWP31                *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2021.02.19                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR41A'
     F*                    PARM           $SHN1   5
     F*                    PARM           $SHN2   5
     F*                    PARM           $SHN3   2
     F*                    PARM           $BOX    4
     F*  IN  $SHN1   5A  IAF PART
     F*      $SHN2   5A  SHIP DATE
     F*      $SHN3   2A  SHIP DATE
     F*  OUT $BOX    4A  # OF BOX
     F******************************************************
     FABTWL31 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C           K#WL31    SETLLABTWL31
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           K#WL31    READEABTWL31                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           W1LPR1    IFEQ $SHN1
     C           W1LPR2    ANDEQ$SHN2
     C           W1LPR3    ANDEQ$SHN3
     C                     ADD  W1CNT     @BOX
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVEL@BOX      $BOX
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *======================================================
      * INITIAL SET
      *======================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $SHN1   5
     C                     PARM           $SHN2   5
     C                     PARM           $SHN3   2
     C                     PARM           $BOX    4
      *
     C           K#WL31    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KSHN1   5
     C                     KFLD           KSHN2   5
     C                     KFLD           KSHN3   2
      *
     C                     MOVEL$SHN1     KSHN1
     C                     MOVEL$SHN2     KSHN2
     C                     MOVEL$SHN3     KSHN3
     C                     MOVEL'0000'    $BOX
     C                     Z-ADD0         @BOX    40
      *
     C                     ENDSR
